          { q: "How do I find an independent kitchen fitter for a supply-only installation?", a: "Ask for referrals from friends, neighbours or your kitchen retailer. Check that the fitter has specific experience with your brand of kitchen, carries public liability insurance, and offers a pre-installation survey before committing to a price." },
