          <p class="mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">For homeowners with a specific style requirement, it is worth checking both brands' ranges in detail. Magnet's showroom presentation makes it easier to visualise how a kitchen will look in the room; Howdens' ranges are typically more familiarly presented through a fitter who can bring samples or show previous work.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 mt-8" style="color: var(--navy);">Installation Experience</h2>
