          <p class="mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">One practical advantage of Howdens is the density and reliability of its depot network. If a component is damaged on delivery or found to be missing on installation morning, a replacement can often be collected from the local depot the same day. Magnet's delivery and replacement process is more centralised, which can occasionally mean a longer wait if something needs to be resolved.</p>

